@Duke_1291 Hi! 
You can have Loose lithium-ion batteries, incl. powerbanks, which have a power of max 100Wh or lithium metal batteries that contain max 2g lithium in your carry-on, and it needs to be within 8 kg as that is the limit for carry on baggage.

//Best regards, Dennis.

@maritza23631525 Hi! 
Yes the refund status tool can't always connect to a travel agency booking, so it still says the case is open. But it has been handled and we have sent a notice to the travel agency. So the best i can recommend is to contact them.

//Best regards, Dennis.

@maritza23631525 Hi! 
Okay your travel agency can call our SAS Helpdesk for more information if they can't see that we have sent them the refund. So the best i can recommend is to contact the travel agency and tell them to call that Helpdesk.

//Best regards, Dennis.

@nygaardbn Hej! 
Det var tråkigt att höra att du fick en sådan upplevelse med vår app. Vi jobbar på att förbättra oss, så tack för att du kontaktade oss angående det.

//Vänlig hälsning, Dennis.

@stokeygurl Hi! 
No problem, you can use this link: https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj and the chat robot should start writing to you, then just write that you want to chat with customer service. 

//Best regards, Dennis.

@stokeygurl Hi! 
I'm sorry that you've had to wait so long, but please contact us via the chatt/messenger of via phone so we can have a look at your mothers booking.

//Best regards, Dennis.

@larssilberbauer Hej! 
Jo vi har ett erbjudande för att ge dig möjlighet att behålla eller uppnå nästa medlemsnivå i SAS EuroBonus ifall man kan tänka sig att resa inom dessa datum, det är dock begränsat i denna situation. Men vi hoppas situationen förbättrar sig.

/Vänlig hälsning, Dennis.

@KClements18 Hello
I am sorry to hear that he has not received refund yet, we are working to ensure that all our customers receives their refund if they are entitled to it. Please contact us on messenger or live chat with booking details and we will take a look at this.
Best regards /Anna

@jakemillington Hello
Contact us on messenger or live chat and we will take a look at this.

Best regards/Anna

@jonasnikolaisen Hej! 
Okej jo det går tyvärr inte att ändra sittplats när man väl kommer in i planet, då det kan göra det svårt att spåra ifall någon skulle bli sjuk efter resan. Men vi försöker alltid erbjuda så gott om plats som möjligt.

//Vänlig hälsning, Dennis.

@Izabellea_ Hello, thank you for contacting us! 
I would like to ask you to contact customer service and we will take a closer look at the rules that apply to your voucher. You can contact us via the contact information on this page: https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj
Kind regards, Anja

@TarquinShepherd Hi TarquinShepherd, please call my colleagues at you local number at the following link under "Customer Service/Eurobonus" for a free rebooking within 10 days from your schedule change.
https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj  

Kind regards, Isak

@chuihsia Hi Chuihsia
The airport staff follow the rules regarding entry restrictions according to the decisions made by the country. It should be updated in the Iata systems at the airport.

Best regards / Anna

@aliageorgia Hi!

We are really sorry for the cancelled flights, we recommend you to take contact with us over the phone and they can help you with looking for alternatives and rebooking the ticket, you can find the local number by this link https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj.

Kind regards, Kevin.

@adeline_deseyne Hi Adeline!

We are really sorry for the long waiting time, we recommend you to take contact with us by chat or phone and we will look in to the matter, you can find the local number by this link https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj.

Kind regards, Kevin

@msmcbrideies Hi!
I recommend you to take contact with us by chat or phone and they will look in to the matter, you can contact us by this link https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj.

Kind regards, Kevin

@DanishDane001 Hi DanishDane001,

Thank you for your question! You can read about our last SAS Airbus A34-300 when flying to the American desert for retirement in this article: https://t.co/OOLT34yz8A

Kind regards Christoffer

@HueyPNewton13 Hello, I am sorry to hear that you did not receive a refund yet. Please contact us by Facebook Messenger, live-chat or phone so we can help you take a look at the refund request. You can find our contact information here: https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Best regards,
Anton.

@patriotennr1 Hej patriotennr1 Detta är länken direkt till vår Facebook sida: https://t.co/ihSNcR2vxO Du ska hitta Facebook Messenger därifrån. Har du inte möjlighet att använda Facebook Messenger på din telefon så kan du även använda en webbläsare. 
Vänliga hälsningar, 
Rebecka

@patriotennr1 Hej!
På facebook hittar du oss under "SAS - Scandinavian Airlines" och vår livechatt samt telefonnumer finner du här: https://t.co/z4gOZAAJQJ
Med vänlig hälsning, Anja

@patriotennr1 Hej! 
Kontakta oss på messenger eller i våran live-chatt så ska vi hjälpa dig med din vocuher.
Med vänlig hälsningar Liv

@bhtorheim Hej!
Extratjänster är normalt sätt inte återbetalbara. Om din bokning däremot blivit avbokad av flygbolaget så har du rätt till att få extratjänsterna återbetalade. 
Med vänlig hälsning, Anja

@irinaki_v Hi!
Contact us on messenger or our live chat and we will help you with your refund.
With kind regards Liv.

@staalec Hej! 
Testa att rensa cache &amp; cookies eller byta till en annan webbläsare.
Med vänlig hälsning Liv.

@IrishmanSteen Hi Steen,
If you follow this link: https://t.co/gml5ZaEizi you can read about the available options right now. If anything changes, we will update the information there.
Best regards, Mikael.

@Elena_Graham Hi! 
I'm glad to hear that you enjoyed your flight with us! Thank you for the report, we hope the situation will get better soon.

//Best regards, Dennis.

@ComRoux Hi! 
I'm sorry about the delay with your refund. I would recommend that you contact our customer service in this case so we can help you have a closer look at it.
https://t.co/b3QIqPBI2R

//Best regards, Dennis.

@nextlevelofme Hej! Vi kan tyvärr inte ta din feedback vidare här från sociala medier men du kan lämna in dina synpunkter till oss via det här webbformuläret: https://t.co/wprQ9Zejqh

Med vänlig hälsning,
Anton.

@ehn Hello, we can not forward information from social media unfortunately. We answer general questions here, to send us feedback you have to use the webform.

Kind regards,
Anton.

@ehn Hello, you can send us feedback through this webform https://t.co/wprQ9Zejqh there is a topic for 'General views' that you can select. Thank you.

Kind regards,
Anton.

@sillehere Hello! We are unfortunately not able to assist with individual cases here on social media. Please contact us via Facebook Messenger or use the contact information here https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj and we will take a look at your refund request.

Kind regards,
Anton.

@ehn Hello! These password requirements are deemed by us to be increasing the safety of the accounts.

Kind regards,
Anton.

@bassen97 Hello. I am sad to hear that it didn't work, please make an error report through this form so we can investigate this further: https://t.co/3JiFn8LBsM

Kind regards,
Anton.

@bassen97 Hello. If you haven't already, please try to clear cache and cookies on chrome to see if that solves the problem.

Kind regards,
Anton.

@rriiicccoo Hello
You can see schedule by this link https://t.co/aWeTBFSc4C or call our customer service to check availability  https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj
Best regards / Anna

@Wrightyp5 Hello
Contact us on messenger or chat and we can help you further with your questions.
Best regards /Anna

@tomdoyle94 Hi! 
I would recommend that you contact our customer service via messenger/chat or by phone so we can help you have a closer look at your refund status. 

//Best regards, Dennis.

@ltenstedt Hej Johanna
Voucher brukar skickas till e-posten som står i bokningen (se gärna i skräpposten utifall den hamnat där) har du inte fått den kontakta oss på messenger så skall vi se på det.
Hälsningar / Anna

@ikra31628601 Hello
Contact us on messenger/chat or phone https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj and we will look at this.
Best regards/ Anna

@theghostofkip Hello
You can find our destinations via this link https://t.co/Wyaoulvd3Q if any questions you are welcome to contact us by chat/messenger or phone https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj 
Best regards / Anna

@Francis90222182 Hi Francis
Contact us by messenger or phone https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj and we can take a look at the refund, we do not recommend to leave personal information on public pages.

Best regards / Anna

@geensmith1 Hi Greensmith1!

Unfortunately we can not see or estimate when we will be planning to operate new routes, I recommend you to take a look at our flight program https://t.co/AGUQlA4HYX to see all the routes we have at the moment.

Kind regards, Kevin

@MrsbNorway Hello
You are welcome to contact us on chat/messenger or phone if you have questions about our services , https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Best regards / Anna
